      "title": "MRI MRCP Scan at Cadabams Diagnostics – Safe, Accurate & Fast",
      "description": "Learn how MRI MRCP at Cadabams Diagnostics helps diagnose bile-duct & pancreas issues—non-invasive, no radiation, quick results, expert care.\n",
